2025-04-16.title: York VS Staffs
2025-04-16.description:
A 6v6 test match between York and Staffs. This served as a test of the Cheep Cheep bot and YouTube streaming.

This match was streamed from both team's perspectives on the UMKL YouTube channel. You can watch those archived streams here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLA9y6mUhnL26e2DXoc9qfiyOymYX5UWHH
